 the memory of the Inuit themselves.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCanadian literature. 0aIndians of North AmericavJuvenile fiction. 0aInuitvJuvenile fiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aHenitiuk, Valerie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMahieu, Marc-Antoine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311127253508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020z978311127473740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978022800501840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780228005018423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780228005018/original  a978-3-11-127253-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-127473-7  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles